{"id":246381,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-甘肃临夏服刑犯马玉忠狱中感染肺结核，/","date":"2012-08-10T13:00:54Z","modified":"2012-08-10T13:00:54Z","title":"维权网 | 甘肃临夏服刑犯马玉忠狱中感染肺结核，生命健康权无保障（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）甘肃省临夏监狱六监区的服刑人员马玉忠，由于监狱方没能及时隔离肺结核病犯，致其在狱中传染上肺结核病，监狱方要求他交纳医疗费用，因马玉忠家境贫寒，导致病情拖延。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>马玉忠，男，回族，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span><span>岁，家住康乐县胭脂镇唐哈村瓦家社</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>号，现在甘肃省临夏监狱六监区服刑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，马玉忠因刑事犯罪被康乐县公安局抓捕，后临夏州中级法院判处有期徒刑十五年，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>投入临夏监狱六监区服刑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在服刑期间，同监舍居住的服刑人员马牙给卜患有严重的肺结核，可是监狱管理方无视相关规定，没有对马牙给卜进行及时的隔离治疗，继续让其同其他服刑人员同吃同住同劳动。期间包括马玉忠在内的多位服刑人员向管理方反映要求将其隔离，没有引起监狱管理方的重视，导致马玉忠和另一名犯人被传染。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>马玉忠被查出肺结核后，监狱方并没有给予及时的治疗隔离，反而要求马玉忠拿出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>千元治疗费。马玉忠家中生活十分困难，无奈让家人借了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>千元交给监狱才被送院治疗，期间已拖延了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7-8</span><span>日。结核病本为重点防控的传染病，需早隔离、早治疗。按中国《监狱法》的规定，服刑人员的医疗费用由国家承担，临夏监狱拒不执行相关法律和政策。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>马玉忠为此多次致信监狱方各级部门、临夏州检察院等申诉，请求监狱方承担责任，对造成的伤害给予赔偿，但都没有任何答复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>马玉忠在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>向卫生部长陈竺、司法部长吴爱英写信反映情况，但他不清楚信是否发出或是否收到回复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>马玉忠希望社会各界对自己的遭遇给予关注，同时关注狱中服刑人员的生命健康权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>马玉忠妻子马兰花电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18219709755</span><span>，　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0930 4483107</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FIclBtE_7CM/UCT-_QC5QoI/AAAAAAAALMg/jZ2qRMVUmOM/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"209\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FIclBtE_7CM/UCT-_QC5QoI/AAAAAAAALMg/jZ2qRMVUmOM/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/--H3uUgDtgzk/UCUAF3HpglI/AAAAAAAALMo/zwIfLJfEFrQ/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/--H3uUgDtgzk/UCUAF3HpglI/AAAAAAAALMo/zwIfLJfEFrQ/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8043036472569265773?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}